title: How to Paint: Commander Farsight
description:
Aggressive and rebellious, Commander Farsight is the master of the Mont’ka, better known as the Killing Blow. We’ll be showing you how to quickly paint his crimson XV-86 Supernova battlesuit in time for the next great battle.

If you're new to painting - check out our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials videos to learn all about it: http://warhammer.me/3Vkojs6
